  <entry>
    <title>shell-sort</title>
    <url>/2020/04/08/shell-sort/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="希尔排序"><a href="#希尔排序" class="headerlink" title="希尔排序"></a>希尔排序</h1><p>学习希尔排序首先要学会插入排序<br>希尔排序算法基本思想：首先定义一个增量对每个数组进行分组，然后对每组数据进行插入排序，对所有组进行插入排序后增量递减（d/=2），直到增量等于1为止。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ShellSort</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[] shellSort(<span class="keyword">int</span>[] arr)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span>[] a = arr;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> len = a.length;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//定义增量为数组的一半，对数组元素进行分组，同增量的算一组</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> d = len/<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//判断增量是否大于1进行循环</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(d &gt; <span class="number">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//增量递减</span></span><br><span class="line">            d /= <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//需要插入排序次数为每组中元素个数</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> x = <span class="number">0</span>;x &lt; d;x++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">//插入排序，增量从1增加到d</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; len - <span class="number">1</span>; i += d) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> j = i + d; j &gt; <span class="number">0</span>; j -= d) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">if</span> (a[j] &lt; a[j - d]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            temp = a[j];</span><br><span class="line">                            a[j] = a[j - d];</span><br><span class="line">                            a[j - d] = temp;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Test</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">testShellSort</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span>[] a = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[]&#123;<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>,<span class="number">11</span>,<span class="number">65</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">9</span>,<span class="number">30</span>,<span class="number">40</span>,<span class="number">30</span>,<span class="number">3</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span>[] rs = shellSort(a);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">assert</span> rs.length &gt; <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;i &lt; rs.length;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(rs[i]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>某些极端情况下，希尔排序最坏时间复杂度仍然是O(n^2)。<br>调整增量为Hibbard增量和Sedgewick增量减少时间复杂度：</p>
<ul>
<li>Hibbard增量<ul>
<li>最坏时间复杂度：O（n^(3/2)）</li>
<li>通项公式 ：2^k-1</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Sedgewick增量<ul>
<li>通项公式：9*4^k - 9*2^k + 1 或者 4^k - 3*2^k + 1</li>
<li>最坏时间复杂度是：（n^(4/3)）</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>algorithm</category>
        <category>java</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>algorithm</tag>
        <tag>java</tag>
        <tag>sort algorithm</tag>
        <tag>shell sort</tag>
      </tags>
